y some fresh air, and take pride in making a visible difference. Gloves, bags, and tools will be provided — just bring your enthusiasm and a willingness to help! All ages welcome. Let’s come together to care for the place we call home.\n\n','9898543345',NULL,'2025-05-19 05:45:22'),(37,' Singing Competition','Competition','Khargone','NavGrah Mandir Khargone','2025-06-04 20:20:00','yes',0.00,'\"Showcase your vocal talent or cheer on your favorite local singers at our Singing Competition! From folk tunes to popular hits, this event celebrates the rich musical diversity of our community. Join us for an evening filled with music, passion, and friendly rivalry.\"\n\n','8956743245',NULL,'2025-05-19 05:48:05'),(38,'Quiz competition','Competition','Indore','Sagun Tower, Vijay Nagar Square, Indore','2025-06-01 09:00:00','no',50.00,'Quiz competition for developing coding skills. Win exciting price above Rs.1000 .','9898543345',NULL,'2025-05-19 14:54:41');
